{"tid":1789080,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂牆黃店認證","createTime":"2019-12-19T07:57:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T03:14:28.000Z","uid":998,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c625f4f313c89fcd53b586760ef1081867bf6a","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家係咪覺得最近無咩連儂牆? 係咪以為個運動降溫? </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔係, 手足仲係日日貼緊</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n但問題係對家都日日清緊, 係近乎每一日都有食環+狗清, 有裝備有人手用公敞。亦有藍絲廢老做。<br />\n<br />\n除左用D難清D的手法去貼外, 更加係需要有新應對手法。<br />\n<br />\n對家其中一個死穴, 就係私人地方外牆, 食環係無權清, 藍絲廢老清係犯刑毀, 張貼人亦可以民事索償及報警。如果大家知度邊度有, 報出來等文宣手足可以查詢授權. <br />\n<br />\n而家黃金經濟圈慢慢成形, 有唔少本來中立以至淺藍鋪頭有意加入, 但又覺得門檻太高，可以考慮下開放外牆及閉店後鐵閘做連儂牆比手足貼文宣, 實體即時認證黃店。好似依間:<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/66359155_2295967553822185_8223586611934265344_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_oc=AQnCYUCZHdM2ZMUjXknMx42fbSva97BiY46rnGG14pymOwUrAilU1XPgVrY_HUbqp5o&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=3c5423dabb5726c8d4239c0cca96be1b&amp;oe=5E7B4E10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F66359155_2295967553822185_8223586611934265344_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_oc%3DAQnCYUCZHdM2ZMUjXknMx42fbSva97BiY46rnGG14pymOwUrAilU1XPgVrY_HUbqp5o%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D3c5423dabb5726c8d4239c0cca96be1b%26oe%3D5E7B4E10&h=1d84b927&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/pcb.2295972970488310/2295967547155519/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.2295972970488310%2F2295967547155519%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=d86Hk5Pgd4X%2FjIl3nTqvfEXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=066708a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/pcb.2295972970488310/2295967547155519/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔使捉鬼, 真心藍店見到想扮黃但日日見到幅連儂牆, 一定精神分裂, 淺藍都係比TVB洗腦多, 睇多D手足文宣有轉化希望. 所以有得貼外牆, 即時認證, 不捉鬼, 不分化!</span>"},{"pid":"86896f050e7141b4a9ba8ac55ace9a25daa51d6d","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b98d420e7f844cfdc3d94201439505b187b5e6d6","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"39119124f7aad46a7888fa3c4bfcab65cffa98f1","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2aaa52e1808d1c2817f438f11ef56e2dd879c14b","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:03:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"dd5381a0a375179ea79ac77eb2435ab306a7408b","tid":1789080,"uid":240149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:06:08.000Z","msg":"借個位嚟推推 高質po 建立黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[突發]即時解決學生溫飽問題 請學生食飯<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776541</a>"},{"pid":"58341a27ae227c9b4685e48d3c2840dfae530c49","tid":1789080,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"push 我見越嚟越多地舖有貼連儂+文宣 要推而廣之"},{"pid":"775b77093d76bad957679e8bc3382f2ce73ebf4b","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58341a27ae227c9b4685e48d3c2840dfae530c49","tid":1789080,"uid":101392,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:08:34.000Z","msg":"push 我見越嚟越多地舖有貼連儂+文宣 要推而廣之"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"正面去解決捉鬼問題, 感化淺藍, 又有文宣效果!"},{"pid":"a0a284f69892ba6d9495c3b740ad8b04bec12d3b","tid":1789080,"uid":998,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"rep